sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as LeaveManagement.API
    participant SVC as LeaveRequestService
    participant BAL as LeaveBalanceService
    participant DB as MySQL
    participant C as Redis

    U->>FE: Submit Leave Request
    FE->>API: POST /api/leaves
    API->>SVC: ApplyAsync(...)
    SVC->>BAL: ValidateSufficientBalanceAsync(...)
    BAL->>DB: Read leave balance
    SVC->>DB: Save leave request
    SVC->>C: Invalidate dashboard/balance cache keys
    API-->>FE: 200 OK
